<p style='margin-right:0in;margin-left:0in;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;'><span style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#0E101A;'>&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin-right:0in;margin-left:0in;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;'><span style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#0E101A;'>Once you complete the mandatory trainings, you must email a copy of your certificates of completion to the DIR HR Training Unit at&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:HRTrainingUnit@dir.ca.gov"><span style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;'>HRTrainingUnit@dir.ca.gov</span></a><span style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#0E101A;'>&nbsp;to receive course credit. &nbsp;You</span><span style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:black;'>&nbsp;cannot participate in DIR&rsquo;s recruitment and hiring process until you have completed these courses.</span></p>
<p style='margin-right:0in;margin-left:0in;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;'><span style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;color:#0E101A;'>&nbsp;</span></p>
